org.dspace.handle

Class MultiRemoteDSpaceRepositoryHandlePlugin

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dspace.handle.MultiRemoteDSpaceRepositoryHandlePlugin
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    net.handle.hdllib.HandleStorage

    public class MultiRemoteDSpaceRepositoryHandlePlugin
extends Object
implements net.handle.hdllib.HandleStorage
    Extension to the CNRI Handle Server that translates requests to resolve handles into remote calls to the mini-DSpace Handle resolver JSON API. This only provides some of the functionality (namely, the resolving of handles to URLs) of the CNRI HandleStorage interface.

    This class is intended to be embedded in the CNRI Handle Server. It conforms to the HandleStorage interface that was delivered with Handle Server version 6.2.0.

    Author:
    Andrea Bollini
